description: This amazing 1+ bed/1 bath penthouse home in the center of South Boston is perfectly located between East and West Broadway! This condo combines convenience, charm, and functionality. The layout is ideal for both everyday living and entertaining, with an open concept living area including an eat-in kitchen and bright living room that has direct access to a private rear deck. The kitchen is updated with stainless steel appliances, white cabinetry, and black granite countertops. This condo also features an updated bathroom including a new vanity, overheard lighting, and hardware. The spacious primary bedroom fits a king-size bed and is filled with natural light. A versatile bonus room sits just off the bedroom and is perfect for a home office, gym, or nursery. This home offers the best of South Boston living with comfort, updates, and incredible private outdoor potential. Additional features include: private basement storage and an opportunity to build a roof deck with panoramic views.
